{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_03_02",
  "title": "LizNoir 03 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……お疲れ様でした\n雑誌の発売、楽しみにしていますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Good work.\nI’m looking forward to the magazine’s release.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.0500000476837155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さあ、莉央、葵、すぐに着替えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Rio‚ Aoi‚ get changed quickly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "endTime": 8.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "次の現場に行くわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and let’s go to our next job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 10.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11,
      "endTime": 13.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.366666666666669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　姫野さん\nこの後はダンスレッスンのはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Himeno-san?\nWe’re supposed to have dance lessons after this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.366666666666669,
      "endTime": 17.58176867167155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "急遽、バラエティ番組からオファーが来たのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got an offer from a variety show at the last minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 20.95340139071147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.15340139071147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "地上波のゴールデンよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s prime time on terrestrial TV!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.15340139071147,
      "endTime": 23.320068057378137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirの知名度を上げるまたとない機会だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a golden opportunity to raise LizNoir’s name recognition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.320068057378144,
      "endTime": 26.95340139071147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.320068057378144
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.153401390711476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "は、はあ\nですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes…\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.153401390711476,
      "endTime": 29.820068057378144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.986734724044812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "霧子、僕と莉央は\n予定通りレッスンに行く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kiriko-san‚ Rio and I\nare going to our lesson as planned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.986734724044812,
      "endTime": 33.413197422027594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.58673472404481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そっちは霧子に任せるよ\n僕達の代わりに面白いことをテキトーに言っといて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll leave that to you.\nJust say whatever’s interesting instead of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.58673472404481,
      "endTime": 38.70637202262879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.920068057378145,
      "endTime": 39.78673472404481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何、馬鹿なことを言ってるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What stupid things are you saying!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7867347240448,
      "endTime": 42.09777792294822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.2867347240448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕達がレッスンして何がいけないの？\n最近霧子が持ってくる仕事の方がよっぽど変だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong with us having a lesson?\nThe jobs you’ve been bringing us lately are way weirder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2867347240448,
      "endTime": 48.70192761421203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.153401390711494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリを控えてる僕達からレッスンの時間を\n奪うなんておかしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To take lesson time away from us when the Grand Prix is right around the corner…\n…that’s weird.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.153401390711494,
      "endTime": 54.25829917589826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.45829917589826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "知名度を上げることも大事なの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Raising our name recognition is important!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.45829917589826,
      "endTime": 57.115441951297605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "貴方達だって有名になれたら嬉しいでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you want to be famous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.124965842564926,
      "endTime": 60.958298985163395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.16782287643072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "知名度なんて必要ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t need any name recognition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.16782287643072,
      "endTime": 63.14532848880407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.34532848880407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "僕達はあくまでも歌とダンスの実力だけでトップになる\nそうだよね？　莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to reach the top with just our singing and dancing skills.\nRight‚ Rio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.34532848880407,
      "endTime": 69.3246483473551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、LizNoirはあくまでも実力で勝ちます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ LizNoir will win with skill alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.51534452979307,
      "endTime": 73.66534443442563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.14867786312641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "（私も本心では葵と同じ気持ちだわ……）\n（でも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I honestly feel the same way as Aoi…)\n(But…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.14867786312641,
      "endTime": 78.63389333630145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.04867786312643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "プロモーションが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you understand how important",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.04867786312643,
      "endTime": 79.94867786312643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どれだけ大切か分からないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "promotion is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9486778631264,
      "endTime": 82.3660702600533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいパフォーマンスさえしてれば勝てるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That naive thought of just needing good performances to win…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.56883666117078,
      "endTime": 84.80216999450411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ナイーブな考え、プロのアイドルとして甘過ぎるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…it’s too naive‚ too complacent for a professional idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.80216999450413,
      "endTime": 88.68241955835705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.16883666117079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "（姫野さんが言うことも分からないわけじゃない）\n（……でも、私達の理想とは違う）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It’s not that I don’t understand what Himeno-san is saying)\n(…but it’s different from our ideal.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.16883666117079,
      "endTime": 95.85779368479139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.0566139016306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく僕達はバラエティには出ないよ\nそんなもの興味ないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ we’re not going on the variety show.\nI’m not interested in that kind of thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0566139016306,
      "endTime": 100.80661371089573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.22328056829723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……姫野さん、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Himeno-san‚ I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.22328056829723,
      "endTime": 103.55795187490735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
